### Get all user ticket preferences
GET {{BASE_URL}}/user-ticket-preferences

### Get a single user ticket preference by ID
GET {{BASE_URL}}/user-ticket-preferences/1

### Create a new user ticket preference
POST {{BASE_URL}}/user-ticket-preferences
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "ticketType": "support",
  "receiveNotifications": true
}

### Update a user ticket preference by ID
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/user-ticket-preferences/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "receiveNotifications": false
}

### Delete a user ticket preference by ID
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/user-ticket-preferences/1
